Packages 
Package Description
obiee.audit.ui
This package contains all classes used to generate result files
obiee.audit.webcat.core
Classes representing out-of-the-box objects in OBIEE
obiee.audit.webcat.engine
Main class and command line arguments processing
obiee.audit.webcat.filters
All FilenameFilter classes used to select specific webcat files
obiee.audit.webcat.objects.shared
Classes in this package represent the bulk of the objects users experience through the UI
obiee.audit.webcat.objects.system
Classes in this package represent system (administration and security) objects in the webcat
obiee.audit.webcat.utils
Utility classes to simplify access to XML data
